TP   Family
CC   This entry represents an N-terminal region (approximately 133-152
CC   residues, positions 6-147) found in YkvP/CgeB family spore proteins.
CC   These proteins contain glycosyltransferase activity and are involved
CC   in bacterial spore formation. The family is found in bacteria,
CC   particularly Bacillota (Paenibacillus, Bacillales) and
CC   Thermodesulfobacteriota (Desulfovibrionia).
